{
  "stem": "26142.14",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "God in heaven, this face from this Jewish girl, I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The deep anguish and her pain, I saw in her eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Some of the girls, she told me, were throwing themselves down the windows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They could not-- down the windows [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the fourth floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "After that happened, they secured the windows that they could not open it anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they also put up a 24-hour guard on the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This poor girl cried with bloody tears, and she asked me and said, if you survive the war, tell our story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Tell the world what these beasts did to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "In truth, it is unfair to the animals to call the German rapists animals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Male animals don't rape female of their own species.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My dear Jewish sister, I'm fulfilling now your request.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I looked into your eyes and I saw and felt your pain, and I still am feeling the pain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I will as long as I'll live.'",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the memoirs that I have written from my experience in the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wrote this here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is what--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wrote this about six years ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] After-- after we spent in Stanislau, we spent about four to six weeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were sent out to all kinds of different works.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We mostly were sent to the station where we did some loading, where the train station were loading material that was going in the direction and in the opposite direction.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were goods going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SIGHS] From Stanislau, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] we were loaded up [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and we were sent [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] to a city closer to the battle line.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
